author: ashtipliyski
body:
Adds event by event comparisons by objects generated by Layer 2 of the calorimeter trigger (CALOL2) which is responsible for jets, e/g, tau and sums.

This PR is a 90x back-port of PR 18397 (https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/18397) as requested by the DQM core team. The DQM changes were applied on top of a fresh installation of CMSSW 9.0.2.
title: Calol2 online dqm 90x
